reviewText: This is a great DVD! My Daughter was not diasspointed. It also has a bonus movie that we already have but she loves watching all the bonus & previews.

This is the second time that I had to write how outrageous the videos are.  One story is how Oscar is a prince and the story line goes into a joke based upon the Gospel of St. Matthew 7:6  and by this Oscar is making fun upon a statement that Our Lord made.
Sesame St. advertises that it helps kids to be kind; but when you get down to it when one makes blasphemy against another's religion that is a hate crime. Into the garbage this goes.  I wish Jim Henson was alive, he produced higher class videos.
Wonderful!  My Grand kids LOVE Elmo so this was a real Christmas treat for them  -  they love watching it over and over and over again!
Grandkids love sesame street, great dvd
My son loves the different stories!
Good movie, two year old loves it
All that really matters is that my granddaughter loves Elmo
